page.title: 09SOUTH NORMANTON 6.00_12.00am
page.content: At 6.00pm. we have our tea. For our tea we have egg,beans,chips and bacon. After we have had our tea we wash the pots. We do not like washing the pots! After we have done them we go outside to play football with our friends.We win usually. We get hungry and so we buy a bag of crisps. Then we go out on our bikes.We have a B.M.X and a Raleigh racer and we go on a B.M.X assault course near Broadmeadows. Occasionally we fall off our bikes. After playing out we have a bath. After that we sit and watch television but soon it is time for bed. We do not like going to bed early but we have to so that we can get up early the following morning. We clean our teeth and get ready for bed.
